TY  - JOUR
T1  - Notes and Comments the Amsterdam Auction
AU  - Goeree, Jacob K.
AU  - Offerman, Theo
Y1  - 2004/01/01
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-0262.2004.00484.x
T2  - Econometrica
